    "message": "<HTML><HEAD><META NAME=\"GENERATOR\" Content=\"Microsoft DHTML Editing Control\"></HEAD><body bgcolor=\"#ffffff\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"New Times Roman\"><DIV><font size=\"2\" face=\"New Times Roman\"><!--MH_BOM--><DIV><font face='Arial' size='2'>Hi \r\nLuke,</DIV><DIV>&nbsp;</DIV><DIV>I hope all is well. I am contacting you about <A href=\"http://www.betterworks.com/\">http://www.betterworks.com/</A>  . I wanted to reach out to you because your experience and expertise aligns with what we are seeking to add to our team here at BetterWorks.</DIV><DIV>&nbsp;</DIV><DIV> We are working on a new company to improve how people work. We have raised 16M from Kleiner Perkins to solve this problem and are&nbsp;working with really amazing customers, like Palantir, Dropbox, Box, Zendesk, Linkedin, and move. More info is on our blog: <A href=\"http://blog.betterworks.com/\">http://blog.betterworks.com/</A>. Our CEO, Kris Duggan worked at Palantir for 3 years and has ben apart of 9 successful startups in Silicon Valley over the last 15 years. His last company Badgeville has a market value of a few hundred million dollars. More info about him here: <SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; \r\n mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA'><A href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/in/krisduggan/\" target=_blank><FONT color=#0000ff>http:/www.linkedin.com/in/krisduggan/</FONT></A></SPAN> &nbsp;&nbsp;Our team is very experienced from Palantir, SFDC, Box, and other SaaS companies. John Doerr from Kleiner and Joe Lonsdale from Palantir are on our Board of Directors.</DIV><DIV> &nbsp;</DIV><DIV>  We have a team of 5 engineers&nbsp;growing to 12 engineers this year, In total we are 15 people growing to 30 this year. We are based in Palo Alto downtown. Our technologies include Django, Angular, D3 and all the modern elements of nimble, flexible, highly productive stack.</DIV><DIV> &nbsp;&nbsp;</DIV><DIV>Wondering if you are interested in exploring this further?</DIV><DIV>&nbsp;</DIV></font><BR><!--MH_SIG--><font face=\"Arial\"><P style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><A name=_MailAutoSig>Thanks,</A><P style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><B>\r\n Crystal Guerrero</B><P style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><B>Technical Recruiter</B></font><!--/MH_SIG--><br><br> <DIV>&nbsp;</DIV><DIV>&nbsp;</DIV><!--MH_EOM--></font></DIV></FONT></body></HTML>",
