    "from": "Dante Cassanego <dante@ahorrandojuntos.com>",
    "id": 49850,
    "message": "<div dir=\"ltr\">Hi Luke,<div><br></div><div><div>It was a pleasure speaking with you at the Stanford Career Fair last Thursday.</div><div><br></div><div>I&#39;ve had a chance to review the conversations and resumes from last week and I&#39;d like to invite you to continue the application process with Juntos.</div>\r\n<div><br></div><div>The next step will be a short phone conversation that explores how we think about software development at Juntos and the relevant background / interests you have.</div><div><br></div><div>I have broad availability this Thursday and Friday you have 30 minutes on those days.</div>\r\n<div><br></div><div>Thanks,</div><div>Dante</div><div><br></div>-- <br><div dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"color:rgb(102,102,102)\"><font face=\"verdana, sans-serif\">Dante Cassanego</font></span><div><font face=\"verdana, sans-serif\"><font color=\"#666666\">CTO &amp; CoFounder | <a href=\"http://ahorrandojuntos.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Juntos Finanzas</a></font><br style=\"color:rgb(102,102,102)\">\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color:rgb(102,102,102)\"><a href=\"http://twitter.com/dantec\" target=\"_blank\">@dantec</a>\u00a0| <a href=\"tel:650.488.7576\" value=\"+16504887576\" target=\"_blank\">650.488.7576</a></span></font></div></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n",
