    "cc": "Irena Pashchenko <Irena.Pashchenko@zazzle.com>, Pamela Bildsoe\r\n\t<Pamela.Bildsoe@zazzle.com>",
    "date": "Tue, 22 Apr 2014 17:42:14 +0000",
    "from": "Taylor Suarez <Taylor.Suarez@zazzle.com>",
    "id": 49854,
    "message": "<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=us-ascii\">\r\n</head>\r\n<body style=\"word-wrap: break-word; -webkit-nbsp-mode: space; -webkit-line-break: after-white-space; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">\r\n<div>Hi Luke!</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>We look forward to meeting you on Tuesday April 29th at 9:30am. Please reply to my email to confirm the interview.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThe interview will be in our Redwood City office located in the Pacific Shores Center. 1800 Seaport Blvd, Redwood City. When you reach the Pacific Shores Center take a right. The 1800 building is the 4th large building. Please sign in and let reception know\r\n that you have an interview. If you have any questions please call the front desk at 650-261-3379.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nFrom the North <br>\r\nTake Highway 101 South <br>\r\nExit Woodside Rd./ Seaport Blvd. ramp <br>\r\nFollow signs for Seaport Blvd. <br>\r\nKeep left at the fork and merge onto Seaport Blvd., heading East <br>\r\nContinue straight on Seaport Blvd. to the end of the road <br>\r\n<br>\r\nFrom the South <br>\r\nTake Highway 101 North <br>\r\nExit Woodside Rd./ Seaport Blvd. ramp <br>\r\nFollow signs for Seaport Blvd. <br>\r\nKeep right at the fork and merge onto Seaport Blvd., heading East <br>\r\nContinue straight on Seaport Blvd. to the end of the road <br>\r\n<br>\r\nYou will be meeting with Lisa Nakano, Ben Ilegbodu, Parker Bossier, Irena Pashchenko, and Rachel Lopatin and should block off the day up to around 2:00pm but please note that who you will be meeting and the length of conversations are subject to change.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>Thanks!</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 18px; font-family: Georgia, serif;\"><img width=\"32\" height=\"32\" id=\"Picture_x0020_3\" src=\"cid:CF0ED740-8740-4835-B694-6776E90ADB92\" alt=\"Macintosh HD:Users:jeremy.britton:Desktop:circleZ.jpg\" type=\"image/png\"><br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; line-height: 25px; font-family: Georgia, serif;\">Taylor P. Suarez</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 18px; font-family: Georgia, serif;\"><br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 16px; font-family: Georgia, serif; color: gray;\">Executive Administration, Zazzle</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 18px; font-family: Georgia, serif;\"><br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 16px; font-family: Georgia, serif; color: gray;\">(650) 261-3379</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n",
