    "from": "\"Rachael Hughes\" <notification@jobvite.com>",
    "id": 50127,
    "message": "<html><head>\r\n<meta http-equiv=Content-Type content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"><style>\r\n.bodyblack { font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; }\r\n.small { font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; }\r\ntd { font-size: 12px; }\r\n.footer { font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; }\r\n</style>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<table cellSpacing=\"0\" cellPadding=\"0\" width=\"450\" border=\"0\" class=\"bodyblack\">\r\n<tr><td><p>Dear Luke,<br /><br />We have modified your interview schedule (end portion) for the Frontend (UI) Developer position as follows: 05/06/2014 09:00 AM to 01:45 PM (Pacific Standard Time).<br /><br />You will be interviewing with:<br />Danny Cochran,Pinar Yilmaz,Abhishek Gupta,Cindy Zhang,Josh Lewis,Lawrence Spracklen,Raj Singh<br /><br /> <table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"> <tbody> <tr> <td>Danny Cochran\u00a0</td> <td>5/6/2014 9:00 AM - 9:45 AM\u00a0</td> <td></td> <td>Engineering Room</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Pinar Yilmaz\u00a0</td> <td>5/6/2014 9:45 AM - 10:30 AM\u00a0</td> <td></td> <td>Engineering Room</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Abhishek Gupta\u00a0</td> <td>5/6/2014 10:30 AM - 11:15 AM\u00a0</td> <td></td> <td>Engineering Room</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Cindy Zhang\u00a0</td> <td>5/6/2014 11:15 AM - 12:00 PM\u00a0</td> <td></td> <td>Engineering Room</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Josh Lewis\u00a0</td> <td>5/6/2014 12:00 PM - 1:00 PM\u00a0</td> <td></td> <td>Interview/Lunch - Deli</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Lawrence Spracklen\u00a0</td> <td>5/6/2014 1:00 PM - 1:30 PM\u00a0</td> <td></td> <td>Engineering Room</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Raj Singh\u00a0</td> <td>5/6/2014 1:30 PM - 1:45 PM\u00a0</td> <td></td> <td>Engineering Room</td> </tr> </tbody> </table> <br /><br />Our Address is:<br /><br />4400 Bohannon Drive<br />Suite #200<br />Menlo Park, CA 94025<br /><br />Contact Emails: <br /><br />rachael@ayasdi.com<br />raj@ayasdi.com<br />joe@ayasdi.com<br /><br /><br />Best regards,<br /><br />Rachael Hughes<span class=\"small\"><br /><hr>You can reply directly to this message or click the following link:<br><a href=\"https://hire.jobvite.com/l?inzEWLowN\">https://hire.jobvite.com/l?inzEWLowN</a><br><br>You can change your email preferences at:<br><a href=\"https://hire.jobvite.com/l?ksRKF0gw1\">https://hire.jobvite.com/l?ksRKF0gw1</a></span></p><br></td></tr>\r\n</table></body></html>",
