    "id": 50142,
    "message": "<html><head><meta http-equiv=\"content-type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"></head><body dir=\"auto\"><div>Hi Luke, as far as other meetings, Rick and I are meeting with David Ngo on Thursday at 2:30 PM, after our meeting with Sofia. Would be great if you could join us, I didn't ask you initially because I wanted to be careful about your time.</div><div><br></div><div>Also on Wednesday at 4 PM, David Carreon and I are meeting with David Kim. You're welcome to join us, even though you're not on the project, if you think it would be interesting and educational. Also it would be nice to have another set of eyes looking at the problem.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>Regardless, it'll be great to see you this week. I'll look forward to hearing about your successes on the interview market</div><div><br></div><div>Brad<br><br>Sent from my iPhone</div><div><br>On May 5, 2014, at 3:49 PM, Luke Knepper &lt;<a href=\"mailto:lukeknepper@gmail.com\">lukeknepper@gmail.com</a>&gt; wrote:<br><br></div><blockquote type=\"cite\"><div><div dir=\"ltr\">Hey Brad,<div><br></div><div>Sounds cool, I'm potentially available (trying to figure out some interview stuff). Do you know what time?</div><div><br></div><div>We have the meeting with Dave Ngo on Friday AM, and the meeting with Sophia on Thursday. Any others? Wednesday or Friday afternoon?</div>\r\n<div><br></div><div>Enjoy your trip out!</div><div><br></div><div>Luke</div></div><div class=\"gmail_extra\"><br><br><div class=\"gmail_quote\">On Sun, May 4, 2014 at 4:54 PM, Brad Gmail <span dir=\"ltr\">&lt;<a href=\"mailto:bradleywright777@gmail.com\" target=\"_blank\">bradleywright777@gmail.com</a>&gt;</span> wrote:<br>\r\n<blockquote class=\"gmail_quote\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex\">Hello Luke, on Thursday morning, I am meeting with John, Rick, and David. We will be doing some long-term planning for soul pulse.<br>\r\n\r\n<br>\r\nIf you would like to join us, it would be great to have you. I know that you have classes, and are very busy. So no worries if not, just wanted to invite you.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nI will see you later this week,<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBrad<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSent from my iPhone</blockquote></div><br></div>\r\n</div></blockquote></body></html>",
