    "id": 50175,
    "message": "<html><head><meta http-equiv=\"content-type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"></head><body dir=\"auto\"><div>Hello,</div><div><br></div><div>We have meetings this week. Thursday, at 2:30, to discuss the pastor tracking app.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>Friday at 10 am to discuss the gratitude app.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>Why don't we plan to meet at Menlo Park Presbyterian Church. Would that work for you all?</div><div><br></div><div>Very much looking forward to the learning and moving these important apps forward!</div><div><br></div><div>Brad</div><div><br>Sent from my iPhone</div><div><br>On Apr 15, 2014, at 1:58 PM, \"David Ngo\" &lt;<a href=\"mailto:behaviordesigns@gmail.com\">behaviordesigns@gmail.com</a>&gt; wrote:<br><br></div><blockquote type=\"cite\"><div>\r\n<div>Great meeting today guys.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><br></div>\r\n<div>Looking forward to meeting you in May Brad.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><br></div>\r\n<div>Sad face @ this being Luke's last meeting.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"mailbox_signature\">\u2014<br>David Ngo<br>Sent from a tiny keyboard</div>\r\n<br><br><div class=\"gmail_quote\"><p>On Tue, Apr 15, 2014 at 1:00 PM, David Ngo <span dir=\"ltr\">&lt;<a href=\"mailto:david@behaviordesigns.com\" target=\"_blank\">david@behaviordesigns.com</a>&gt;</span> wrote:<br></p><blockquote class=\"gmail_quote\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex;\">\r\n<div dir=\"ltr\">Hey Luke &amp; Brad!<div><br></div>\r\n<div>Talk to y'all soon.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><br></div>\r\n<div>In case y'all didn't get the link to the google doc for today's call:</div>\r\n<div><br></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1eCTm1DO87NOuNoIFo8FSDU-izhi0bXCZSe-PyHI-6C0/edit\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1eCTm1DO87NOuNoIFo8FSDU-izhi0bXCZSe-PyHI-6C0/edit</a><br></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"gmail_extra\">\r\n<br><br><div class=\"gmail_quote\">On Mon, Apr 14, 2014 at 7:11 PM, bradley Wright <span dir=\"ltr\">&lt;<a href=\"mailto:bradleywright777@gmail.com\">bradleywright777@gmail.com</a>&gt;</span> wrote:<br><blockquote class=\"gmail_quote\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex\">\r\n<div dir=\"ltr\">Hello Luke,<div><br></div>\r\n<div>I love the look of the report... lots of bright colors and a spacious layout.</div>\r\n<div><br></div>\r\n<div>Tomorrow at 10 pdt/ 1 edt would work for me. Look forward to talking with you both,</div>\r\n\r\n<div><br></div>\r\n<div>Brad</div>\r\n<div><br></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"HOEnZb\"><div class=\"h5\">\r\n<div class=\"gmail_extra\">\r\n<br><br><div class=\"gmail_quote\">On Sun, Apr 13, 2014 at 11:37 PM, Luke Knepper <span dir=\"ltr\">&lt;<a href=\"mailto:lukeknepper@gmail.com\">lukeknepper@gmail.com</a>&gt;</span> wrote:<br><blockquote class=\"gmail_quote\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex\">\r\n<div dir=\"ltr\">Hey Brad and David,<div><br></div>\r\n<div>I've finished my draft of the new report! It's different from the mock I sent, and it should hopefully be very simple and easy to understand. Check it out here...</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<a href=\"http://soulpulse.org/report/dev.html\">http://soulpulse.org/report/dev.html</a><br></div>\r\n<div><br></div>\r\n<div>If you want to see it with your SoulPulse data, log in to SoulPulse and then go to&nbsp;<a href=\"http://soulpulse.org/report/dev.php\">http://soulpulse.org/report/dev.php</a>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div><br></div>\r\n<div>note: It's missing the animated timeline Isaac created, which will go at the top (I'm asking him if he has time to integrate it).</div>\r\n<div><br></div>\r\n<div>Please let me know your thoughts, and any ideas for things that could be added. Right now it might err on the side of oversimplicity, as it has no interactivity and the graphs are very basic (perhaps repetitive) -- if you have any brilliant ideas, do share.</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div><br></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<b>Scheduling a time to Skype -- </b>Brad, David and I are planning to Skype this Tuesday, 1pm eastern (10am PST). Does that work for you? I know you want to be in on the call, so want to make sure we picked a good time.</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div><br></div>\r\n<div>David -- let me know if there's anything more I can do to prepare for our meeting. I'm thinking we just focus on making the report as cool as possible.</div>\r\n<div><br></div>\r\n<div>Talk soon,</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div><br></div>\r\n<div>Luke</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n</div>\r\n<br></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n</div>\r\n<br><br clear=\"all\"><div><br></div>-- <br><div dir=\"ltr\">\r\n<div style=\"color:rgb(136,136,136)\">\r\n<span style=\"border-collapse:collapse;font-family:Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-family:garamond,serif\"><font color=\"#3333ff\"><a href=\"http://twitter.com/dngoo\" style=\"color:rgb(17,85,204)\">David Ngo</a></font></span></b></span><span style=\"border-collapse:collapse;font-family:Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-family:garamond,serif\"><font color=\"#888888\">&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://bit.ly/behaviordesignmajor\" style=\"color:rgb(17,85,204)\">Stanford University '13</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://behaviordesigns.com/\" style=\"color:rgb(17,85,204)\">Behavior Designs&nbsp;</a></font></span></b></span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"color:rgb(136,136,136)\">\r\n<span style=\"border-collapse:collapse;font-family:Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-family:garamond,serif\"><font color=\"#888888\">\"the trouble is, you think you have time.</font></span></b></span><b style=\"font-family:Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:garamond,serif\"><font color=\"#888888\">\" --buddha &nbsp;<font size=\"4\">&nbsp;</font></font></span></b>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</blockquote></div><br></div></blockquote></body></html>",
