    "message": "<div dir=\"ltr\">Chris,<div><br></div><div>Thanks for the information. \u00a0I made reservations for the weekend for Mike and his boys and for me, just in case I can come. \u00a0They were very nice on the phone and no problems. \u00a0They said that the cancellation date is not July 8th, but August 6th, which is great for me. \u00a0By that time, I will definitely know if I can be there. \u00a0</div>\r\n<div><br></div><div>The only part of your information that I thought was a little confusing was the second and third paragraph in which La Quinta and Cattin Waters were mentioned. \u00a0Are those other hotels? \u00a0If so, perhaps a note that they are alternative hotels to choose from should be included in your email.</div>\r\n<div><br></div><div>Luke and Bethany: I would like to put my cousin, Greg Stott, on your guest list if possible. \u00a0His address is:</div><div>2711 State Highway6 146 South, Livingston, TDX 77351</div><div><br></div><div>Love,</div>\r\n<div><br></div><div>Mom</div></div><div class=\"gmail_extra\"><br><br><div class=\"gmail_quote\">On Wed, May 7, 2014 at 4:08 PM, chris knepper <span dir=\"ltr\">&lt;<a href=\"mailto:csknepper@gmail.com\" target=\"_blank\">csknepper@gmail.com</a>&gt;</span> wrote:<br>\r\n<blockquote class=\"gmail_quote\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex\"><div dir=\"ltr\">Hi! We&#39;ve blocked off some rooms for Bethany and Luke&#39;s wedding and we wanted you to know how to reserve a room at the special rate we&#39;ve negotiated. Here are the details:<div>\r\n<br></div><div><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1QaZW_TRY4nuTLBuIeqf-0uRVLM9w4vnRbQ4RnnahWYE\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1QaZW_TRY4nuTLBuIeqf-0uRVLM9w4vnRbQ4RnnahWYE</a></div>\r\n<div><br></div><div>We&#39;re sending this to a small group right now to &quot;test&quot; out the reservation process. Let us know if the process works for you and we&#39;ll then send it out to more people.<br clear=\"all\">\r\n\r\n<div><br></div><div>Love to all!</div><span class=\"HOEnZb\"><font color=\"#888888\">-- <br><br><div>-Chris</div><div><br></div><div>cell: <a href=\"tel:703-419-0231\" value=\"+17034190231\" target=\"_blank\">703-419-0231</a> \u00a0| \u00a0<a href=\"http://twitter.com/csknepper\" target=\"_blank\">twitter.com/csknepper</a></div>\r\n<div><br></div>\r\n</font></span></div></div>\r\n</blockquote></div><br></div>\r\n",
