    "message": "<div dir=\"ltr\">The eagle is in the nest.</div><div class=\"gmail_extra\"><br clear=\"all\"><div><div dir=\"ltr\"><div>Tom</div>\r\n<div>+86-1550-1087-167</div><div><br></div><div>&quot;The heavens declare the glory of God; the skies proclaim the works of his hands.&quot; Psalm 19:1</div></div></div>\r\n<br><br><div class=\"gmail_quote\">On 11 May 2014 09:14, Luke Knepper <span dir=\"ltr\">&lt;<a href=\"mailto:lukeknepper@gmail.com\" target=\"_blank\">lukeknepper@gmail.com</a>&gt;</span> wrote:<br><blockquote class=\"gmail_quote\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex\">\r\n<div dir=\"ltr\">Thanks so much, guys! I hugely appreciate it. This means a lot. I reminded Bethany to give y&#39;all the envelope (please ask for it if she forgets)<div><br></div><div>Have a great Sunday,</div><div>Luke</div>\r\n\r\n</div><div class=\"HOEnZb\"><div class=\"h5\"><div class=\"gmail_extra\"><br><br><div class=\"gmail_quote\">On Fri, May 9, 2014 at 11:45 PM, Mike Gropp <span dir=\"ltr\">&lt;<a href=\"mailto:gropp.mike@gmail.com\" target=\"_blank\">gropp.mike@gmail.com</a>&gt;</span> wrote:<br>\r\n\r\n<blockquote class=\"gmail_quote\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex\"><div dir=\"ltr\">Also sorry for late reply, count me in. I can tag team with Tom!</div><div><div>\r\n<div class=\"gmail_extra\"><br><br><div class=\"gmail_quote\">On Sat, May 10, 2014 at 12:56 PM, Tom Maj <span dir=\"ltr\">&lt;<a href=\"mailto:tomamaj@gmail.com\" target=\"_blank\">tomamaj@gmail.com</a>&gt;</span> wrote:<br>\r\n<blockquote class=\"gmail_quote\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex\"><div dir=\"ltr\">Sorry for the late reply but YES I can do that. I&#39;ll try to drop in Sunday afternoon or possibly could give them to her at church after lunch?</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"gmail_extra\"><br clear=\"all\"><div><div dir=\"ltr\">\r\n<div>Tom</div>\r\n<div><a href=\"tel:%2B86-1550-1087-167\" value=\"+8615501087167\" target=\"_blank\">+86-1550-1087-167</a></div><div><br></div><div>&quot;The heavens declare the glory of God; the skies proclaim the works of his hands.&quot; Psalm 19:1</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div></div><div><div>\r\n<br><br><div class=\"gmail_quote\">On 7 May 2014 11:49, Luke Knepper <span dir=\"ltr\">&lt;<a href=\"mailto:lukeknepper@gmail.com\" target=\"_blank\">lukeknepper@gmail.com</a>&gt;</span> wrote:<br><blockquote class=\"gmail_quote\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div dir=\"ltr\">Hey Tom &amp; Mike,<div><br></div><div>How are things in Beijing? I miss it there, wish I could be back playing Catan with y&#39;all. California is cool but my life is full of work and busyness.</div><div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n</div><div>Quick request: I remember one/both of you saying that you&#39;d possibly be down to get Bethany some flowers from time to time. Would you perchance have time to get some and give them to her this weekend? (Don&#39;t worry, it&#39;s not for Mother&#39;s day... I just think she could use some flowers.) No worries if not!</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div><br></div><div>I left Bethany with an envelope with your names on it that has 100 kuai -- I hope it will be good for two batches (though that might be a stretch...). She&#39;s not picky. Her favorite colors right now are coral (kind of a pinkish redish orange) and white and green. There are tons of places to buy them, my favorite was the lady on BLCU near the side-gate by DongWangZhuang.</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div><br></div><div>Again, no worries if y&#39;all are too busy -- and thanks so much for considering it! Would be a big help.</div><div><br></div><div>Tom -- hope the preparations to move are going smoothly.</div><div>Mike -- hope the iPad business is soaring!</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div><br></div><div>Blessings,</div><div>Luke</div></div>\r\n</blockquote></div><br></div></div></div>\r\n</blockquote></div><br></div>\r\n</div></div></blockquote></div><br></div>\r\n</div></div></blockquote></div><br></div>\r\n",
