    "cc": null,
    "date": "Wed, 14 May 2014 15:27:06 +0000",
    "from": "\"STEVENS, GREGORY\" <gs7333@att.com>",
    "id": 50313,
    "message": "<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=Windows-1252\">\r\n</head>\r\n<body style=\"word-wrap: break-word; -webkit-nbsp-mode: space; -webkit-line-break: after-white-space; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">\r\n<div>Hi Luke,</div>\r\n<div>I know we\u2019ve tried numerous times to connect with you after the Stanford Job Fair. &nbsp;Are you still interested in AT&amp;T? &nbsp;If so, one of the directors in the SF office would like to set up days and times to interview you. &nbsp;Let me know what you think.</div>\r\n<div>Thanks,</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><font class=\"Apple-style-span\" color=\"#000000\"><font class=\"Apple-style-span\" face=\"Calibri\">Greg Stevens</font></font></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(31, 73, 125);\">AT&amp;T Big Data- Technical Recruiter<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(31, 73, 125);\">Phone: (650) 779-5178<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(31, 73, 125);\">Email:&nbsp;<span style=\"color: blue;\"><a href=\"mailto:rshirazi@att.com\" style=\"color: purple;\">g</a>s7333@att.com</span></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n",
