    "message": "<html><head></head><body style=\"word-wrap: break-word; -webkit-nbsp-mode: space; -webkit-line-break: after-white-space; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; \"><div><div><div>&nbsp;</div></div></div><span id=\"OLK_SRC_BODY_SECTION\"><div style=\"word-wrap: break-word; -webkit-nbsp-mode: space; -webkit-line-break: after-white-space; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; \"><span id=\"OLK_SRC_BODY_SECTION\"><div style=\"word-wrap: break-word; -webkit-nbsp-mode: space; -webkit-line-break: after-white-space; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; \"><span id=\"OLK_SRC_BODY_SECTION\"><div style=\"word-wrap: break-word; -webkit-nbsp-mode: space; -webkit-line-break: after-white-space; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; \"><div><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Hi Luke,</span></div><div><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\"><br></span></div><div>You have great front-end experience and I love your intern project at Palantir building a tool for their health team.</div></div></span><div><br></div><span id=\"OLK_SRC_BODY_SECTION\"><div style=\"word-wrap: break-word; -webkit-nbsp-mode: space; -webkit-line-break: after-white-space; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; \"><div><div style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: none; \"><div style=\"font-size: medium; font-family: Calibri; \"><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; \">In 2013 shopkick generated over 500 million dollars of sales to our partners by driving millions of users into\r\n stores per month! &nbsp;Now we are building on top of our location aware beacons and retail partnerships to create a unique shopping experience in the physical world. We are empowering shoppers with the information they need--price, deals, rewards, availability,\r\n popularity--inside the store itself.</span><br style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; \"><br style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; \"><span style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; \">With our team of 20 engineers, this journey is just starting. Would you be open to a quick 10 minute chat to explore our engineering opportunities ? &nbsp;Check out the links below to understand our massive impact!</span><br style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; \"><br style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; \"><a href=\"http://tech.fortune.cnn.com/2014/02/28/apples-ibeacon-signals-turning-point-for-mobile-engagement/?utm_content=buffer56813&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=twitter.com&amp;utm_campaign=buffer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; \">http://tech.fortune.cnn.com/2014/02/28/apples-ibeacon-signals-turning-point-for-mobile-engagement/?utm_content=buffer56813&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=twitter.com&amp;utm_campaign=buffer</a><br style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; \"><br style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; \"><a href=\"http://www.bizreport.com/2013/02/nielsen-ranks-shopkick-top-real-world-shopping-mobile-app.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; \">http://www.bizreport.com/2013/02/nielsen-ranks-shopkick-top-real-world-shopping-mobile-app.html</a><br style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; \"><br style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; \"><a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m9by4vjWSfU\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; \">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m9by4vjWSfU</a><br style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; \"><br style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; \"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EXasElJ09Ls\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; \">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EXasElJ09Ls</a><br style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; \"><br style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; \"></span></div><div style=\"font-size: medium; font-family: Calibri; \"><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Best,</span></div><div style=\"font-size: medium; font-family: Calibri; \"><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Shathiya</span></div><div><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\"><br></span></div></div></div><div><div><div><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Shathiya Narayanasamy</span></div><div><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Engineering Recruiter|shopkick</span></div><div><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\"><a href=\"mailto:Shathiya@shopkick.com\">Shathiya@shopkick.com</a></span></div></div><div><br></div></div></div></span></div></span></div></span></body></html>\r\n",
