  "50343": {
    "categorized": true,
    "category": 1,
    "cc": null,
    "date": "Thu, 15 May 2014 16:29:13 +0000",
    "from": "Xander Pollock <xanderp@google.com>",
    "id": 50343,
    "message": "How did the Houzz interview go? and Dropbox? Where&#39;s your project at?<br><br><div>On Mon Apr 28 2014 at 10:41:20 PM, Luke Knepper &lt;<a href=\"mailto:lukeknepper@gmail.com\">lukeknepper@gmail.com</a>&gt; wrote:</div><blockquote class=\"gmail_quote\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex\">\r\n\r\n<span>We&#39;re focusing on web. Might get to do some native stuff down the line but not for a while. Thanks for the intro!<div><br></div>\r\n<div>Cool about your Houzz friend -- would be great to talk if the interview goes well.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div><br></div>\r\n<div>Thursday at noon is perfect! Looking forward to it.\u00a0</div></span><div>\u2014<br>Sent from <a href=\"https://www.dropbox.com/mailbox\" target=\"_blank\">Mailbox</a>\r\n</div>\r\n<br><br><div class=\"gmail_quote\"><p>On Mon, Apr 28, 2014 at 3:24 PM, Xander Pollock <span dir=\"ltr\">&lt;<a href=\"mailto:xanderp@google.com\" target=\"_blank\">xanderp@google.com</a>&gt;</span> wrote:<br></p><blockquote class=\"gmail_quote\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex\">\r\n\r\n<p>Awesome. Web only? If so, I&#39;ll introduce you to Aleem, the founder at Streak.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div><br></div>\r\n<div>I have a friend (designer) who worked at Houzz and very closely with the founders who can give you the inside scoop if you&#39;d like. After your interview would probably be better.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div><br></div>\r\n<div>I can meet you this Thursday. How about here at 12pm?\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>1900 Charleston, Mountain View CA<br><br><div>\u00a0<br></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br><div>On Mon Apr 28 2014 at 12:10:49 PM, Luke Knepper &lt;<a href=\"mailto:lukeknepper@gmail.com\" target=\"_blank\">lukeknepper@gmail.com</a>&gt; wrote:</div>\r\n<blockquote class=\"gmail_quote\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex\">\r\n<span>Hey!<div><br></div>\r\n<div>It was great to see you too. Yep the project is approved and in motion. We are building an email client that we want to integrate with Gmail (like Mailbox). Would love to be hooked up with some advice.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div><br></div>\r\n<div>I&#39;d love to get lunch! On Friday I&#39;m interviewing at Houzz. I could do Thursday, or next week.\u00a0</div></span><div>\u2014<br>Sent from <a href=\"https://www.dropbox.com/mailbox\" target=\"_blank\">Mailbox</a>\r\n</div>\r\n<br><br><div class=\"gmail_quote\">\r\n<p>On Fri, Apr 25, 2014 at 11:56 AM, Xander Pollock <span dir=\"ltr\">&lt;<a href=\"mailto:xanderp@google.com\" target=\"_blank\">xanderp@google.com</a>&gt;</span> wrote:<br></p>\r\n<blockquote class=\"gmail_quote\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex\">\r\n\r\n<p>Hey Luke!\u00a0</p>\r\n<div><br></div>\r\n<div>It was great seeing you at Google, and talking at breakfast.<br><br>Did you guys get your project approved yet? I&#39;ll connect you with Aleem at Streak if it is.\u00a0<div><br></div>\r\n<div>Do you want to come by for lunch next week? I have time on Friday.\u00a0<div>\r\n<br></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br><div>On Mon Apr 07 2014 at 10:29:00 PM, Luke Knepper &lt;<a href=\"mailto:lukeknepper@gmail.com\" target=\"_blank\">lukeknepper@gmail.com</a>&gt; wrote:</div>\r\n<blockquote class=\"gmail_quote\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex\">\r\n<div dir=\"ltr\">Hey Xander, It&#39;s Luke from the basement of Huang yesterday.\u00a0<div><br></div>\r\n<div>Just want to say that it was awesome to meet you! It felt very providential, thanks so much for reaching out and offering help. We&#39;re having trouble getting our project idea approved, so we may not end up getting to do the email client after all... If we do, then I&#39;d love to get connected with the Streak CRM guy or anyone else who could help us get started.<div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<br></div>\r\n<div>Also, Daniel said that you go to Grace -- so cool! I&#39;ve been wanting to check out Grace for a while now (been going to Sanctuary).</div>\r\n<div><br></div>\r\n<div>If you&#39;re up for it, it would be awesome to get a meal together and hear about life / faith at Google and as a UX Designer. (lunch T/Th or any breakfast / dinner works for me)</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br></div>\r\n<div>Thanks &amp; blessings,</div>\r\n<div><br></div>\r\n<div>Luke</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n</div>\r\n<br></blockquote>\r\n</blockquote></div><br></blockquote>\r\n",
    "predicted": true,
    "read": false,
    "subject": "Re: Hey!",
    "to": "Luke Knepper <lukeknepper@gmail.com>"
  },
