    "message": "Thank You for your inquiry...\r\nwe can do a vintage car...\r\n$300 plus 20% service charge... \r\n\r\nthere is a $200 deposit to reserve...\r\n\r\nlet me know if this works for you and I will email paperwork...\r\n\r\nthank you,\r\nRebecca\r\nwww.bluediamondlimos.net\r\n972.870.5413\r\n--------------------------------------------\r\nOn Sat, 5/17/14, Luke Knepper <lukeknepper@gmail.com> wrote:\r\n\r\n Subject: Quote for wedding drive from McKinney to Dallas on August 10th\r\n To: limoquoteplease@yahoo.com\r\n Date: Saturday, May 17, 2014, 10:59 AM\r\n \r\n Hi,\r\n I came across your website and think your cars\r\n are absolutely stunning... My fianc\u00e9 and I are interested\r\n in having a vintage car drive us from our wedding in\r\n McKinney to our hotel in downtown Dallas on August 10th at\r\n 9/10pm -- would you have a car available that night? How\r\n much would it cost?\r\n \r\n Many thanks!\r\n Luke and Bethany\r\n",
