    "message": "<div dir=\"ltr\"><div class=\"gmail_quote\"><div dir=\"ltr\">Hey all --\u00a0<div><br></div><div>Here&#39;s tomorrow&#39;s behavior.\u00a0</div><div><br></div><div>It&#39;s a bonus one. \u00a0Behavior 0.\u00a0</div><div><br></div><div><b style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,0)\">Tomorrow,\u00a0</b></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div>I just want you to be aware of what you do within the first 10 minutes of waking up.\u00a0 <br></div><div><br></div><div><b style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,0)\">Here&#39;s your &lt;2 minute action step to take now:\u00a0</b></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div>change the background of your phone\u00a0</div><div>to create an mental association with this week&#39;s experiment.\u00a0</div><div><br></div><div>You can go back to your old wallpaper after this week.\u00a0</div><div><br></div><div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<b><br></b></div><div><b>Tomorrow night at 6PM PT / 9PM EST,</b> you&#39;ll receive the first behavior.\u00a0<br></div><div><div></div></div></div></div><br>-- <br><div dir=\"ltr\"><div><div style=\"color:rgb(136,136,136)\"><span style=\"border-collapse:collapse;font-family:Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-family:garamond,serif\"><font color=\"#3333ff\"><a href=\"http://twitter.com/dngoo\" style=\"color:rgb(17,85,204)\" target=\"_blank\">David Ngo</a></font></span></b></span><span style=\"border-collapse:collapse;font-family:Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-family:garamond,serif\"><font color=\"#888888\">\u00a0|\u00a0<a href=\"http://bit.ly/behaviordesignmajor\" style=\"color:rgb(17,85,204)\" target=\"_blank\">Stanford University</a>\u00a0|\u00a0<a href=\"http://learnbehaviordesign.com\" style=\"color:rgb(17,85,204)\" target=\"_blank\">Learn Behavior Design</a></font></span></b></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"color:rgb(136,136,136)\"><span style=\"border-collapse:collapse;font-family:Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-family:garamond,serif\"><font color=\"#888888\">&quot;the trouble is, you think you have time.</font></span></b></span><b style=\"font-family:Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:garamond,serif\"><font color=\"#888888\">&quot; --buddha \u00a0<font size=\"4\">\u00a0</font></font></span></b></div>\r\n\r\n</div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n",
