    "from": "Bethany Eden <bethanyjoyeden@gmail.com>",
    "id": 50402,
    "message": "It&#39;s great, let&#39;s get this!<br><br>On Sunday, May 18, 2014, Luke Knepper &lt;<a href=\"mailto:lukeknepper@gmail.com\">lukeknepper@gmail.com</a>&gt; wrote:<br><blockquote class=\"gmail_quote\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex\">\r\n<div dir=\"ltr\">What do you think of this one?<div><br></div><div>I love you.<br><br><div class=\"gmail_quote\">---------- Forwarded message ----------<br>From: <b class=\"gmail_sendername\">Rebecca Harris</b> <span dir=\"ltr\">&lt;<a href=\"javascript:_e(%7B%7D,&#39;cvml&#39;,&#39;limoquoteplease@yahoo.com&#39;);\" target=\"_blank\">limoquoteplease@yahoo.com</a>&gt;</span><br>\r\n\r\nDate: Sat, May 17, 2014 at 12:49 PM<br>Subject: Pricing for wedding drive from McKinney to Dallas on August 10th<br>To: Luke Knepper &lt;<a href=\"javascript:_e(%7B%7D,&#39;cvml&#39;,&#39;lukeknepper@gmail.com&#39;);\" target=\"_blank\">lukeknepper@gmail.com</a>&gt;<br>\r\n<br><br>Thank You for your inquiry...<br>\r\n\r\nwe can do a vintage car...<br>\r\n$300 plus 20% service charge...<br>\r\n<br>\r\nthere is a $200 deposit to reserve...<br>\r\n<br>\r\nlet me know if this works for you and I will email paperwork...<br>\r\n<br>\r\nthank you,<br>\r\nRebecca<br>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.bluediamondlimos.net\" target=\"_blank\">www.bluediamondlimos.net</a><br>\r\n<a href=\"tel:972.870.5413\" value=\"+19728705413\" target=\"_blank\">972.870.5413</a><br>\r\n--------------------------------------------<br>\r\nOn Sat, 5/17/14, Luke Knepper &lt;<a href=\"javascript:_e(%7B%7D,&#39;cvml&#39;,&#39;lukeknepper@gmail.com&#39;);\" target=\"_blank\">lukeknepper@gmail.com</a>&gt; wrote:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0Subject: Quote for wedding drive from McKinney to Dallas on August 10th<br>\r\n\u00a0To: <a href=\"javascript:_e(%7B%7D,&#39;cvml&#39;,&#39;limoquoteplease@yahoo.com&#39;);\" target=\"_blank\">limoquoteplease@yahoo.com</a><br>\r\n\u00a0Date: Saturday, May 17, 2014, 10:59 AM<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0Hi,<br>\r\n\u00a0I came across your website and think your cars<br>\r\n\u00a0are absolutely stunning... My fianc\u00e9 and I are interested<br>\r\n\u00a0in having a vintage car drive us from our wedding in<br>\r\n\u00a0McKinney to our hotel in downtown Dallas on August 10th at<br>\r\n\u00a09/10pm -- would you have a car available that night? How<br>\r\n\u00a0much would it cost?<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0Many thanks!<br>\r\n\u00a0Luke and Bethany<br>\r\n</div><br></div></div>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n",
    "predicted": true,
