    "from": "David Ngo <dngo11@stanford.edu>",
    "id": 50411,
    "message": "<div dir=\"ltr\"><p style=\"margin:0px 0px 6px;color:rgb(20,24,35);font-family:Helvetica,Arial,&#39;lucida grande&#39;,tahoma,verdana,arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.63636302947998px;line-height:17.563634872436523px\">It&#39;s good to be back and writing again.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin:0px 0px 6px;color:rgb(20,24,35);font-family:Helvetica,Arial,&#39;lucida grande&#39;,tahoma,verdana,arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.63636302947998px;line-height:17.563634872436523px\"><span style=\"font-size:13.63636302947998px\"><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n</span></p><p style=\"margin:0px 0px 6px;color:rgb(20,24,35);font-family:Helvetica,Arial,&#39;lucida grande&#39;,tahoma,verdana,arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.63636302947998px;line-height:17.563634872436523px\"><span style=\"font-size:13.63636302947998px\">I know I haven&#39;t sent anything out in a while after you signed up for my newsletter on BehaviorDesigns. \u00a0</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin:0px 0px 6px;color:rgb(20,24,35);font-family:Helvetica,Arial,&#39;lucida grande&#39;,tahoma,verdana,arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.63636302947998px;line-height:17.563634872436523px\"><span style=\"font-size:13.63636302947998px\"><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n</span></p><p style=\"margin:0px 0px 6px;color:rgb(20,24,35);font-family:Helvetica,Arial,&#39;lucida grande&#39;,tahoma,verdana,arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.63636302947998px;line-height:17.563634872436523px\"><span style=\"font-size:13.63636302947998px\">It probably also didn&#39;t help that I</span><span style=\"font-size:13.63636302947998px\">&#39;ve been working on a series of new personal projects as well as soul-growing for the past 10 months.\u00a0</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin:0px 0px 6px;color:rgb(20,24,35);font-family:Helvetica,Arial,&#39;lucida grande&#39;,tahoma,verdana,arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.63636302947998px;line-height:17.563634872436523px\"><br></p><p style=\"margin:0px 0px 6px;color:rgb(20,24,35);font-family:Helvetica,Arial,&#39;lucida grande&#39;,tahoma,verdana,arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.63636302947998px;line-height:17.563634872436523px\">\r\n\r\n\r\nOne of them was moving my blog platform. \u00a0</p><p style=\"margin:0px 0px 6px;color:rgb(20,24,35);font-family:Helvetica,Arial,&#39;lucida grande&#39;,tahoma,verdana,arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.63636302947998px;line-height:17.563634872436523px\">\r\n\r\n\r\nAnother was finally giving myself approval for quality writing that I could share.\u00a0</p><p style=\"margin:0px 0px 6px;color:rgb(20,24,35);font-family:Helvetica,Arial,&#39;lucida grande&#39;,tahoma,verdana,arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.63636302947998px;line-height:17.563634872436523px\">\r\n\r\n\r\n<br>Finally, I&#39;ve accomplished both.\u00a0</p><p style=\"margin:0px 0px 6px;color:rgb(20,24,35);font-family:Helvetica,Arial,&#39;lucida grande&#39;,tahoma,verdana,arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.63636302947998px;line-height:17.563634872436523px\">\r\n\r\n\r\nHere&#39;s the first one that I&#39;m ready to publicly release -- straight from hong kong.</p><p style=\"margin:0px 0px 6px;color:rgb(20,24,35);font-family:Helvetica,Arial,&#39;lucida grande&#39;,tahoma,verdana,arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.63636302947998px;line-height:17.563634872436523px\">\r\n\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13.63636302947998px\"><br></span></p><p style=\"margin:0px 0px 6px;color:rgb(20,24,35);font-family:Helvetica,Arial,&#39;lucida grande&#39;,tahoma,verdana,arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.63636302947998px;line-height:17.563634872436523px\">\r\n\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13.63636302947998px\">I think you&#39;ll enjoy it.\u00a0</span></p><div style=\"display:inline;color:rgb(20,24,35);font-family:Helvetica,Arial,&#39;lucida grande&#39;,tahoma,verdana,arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.63636302947998px;line-height:17.563634872436523px\">\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin:0px 0px 6px\">Spoiler: it has nothing to do with hong kong.</p><p style=\"margin:0px 0px 6px\"><br></p><p style=\"margin:0px 0px 6px\">Read my debut post here:</p><p style=\"margin:0px 0px 6px\"><a href=\"http://www.davidngo.me/blog/2014/5/13/the-opposite-of-external-validation-is-giving-permission\" target=\"_blank\">\u00a0&quot;The Opposite of External Validation is Giving Permission.&quot;</a></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div><div><br></div>-- <br><div dir=\"ltr\"><div><div style=\"color:rgb(136,136,136)\"><span style=\"border-collapse:collapse;font-family:Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-family:garamond,serif\"><font color=\"#3333ff\"><a href=\"http://www.davidngo.me\" style=\"color:rgb(17,85,204)\" target=\"_blank\">David Ngo</a></font></span></b></span><span style=\"border-collapse:collapse;font-family:Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-family:garamond,serif\"><font color=\"#888888\">\u00a0|\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/dngoo\" style=\"color:rgb(17,85,204)\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a>\u00a0|\u00a0<a href=\"http://learnbehaviordesign.com\" style=\"color:rgb(17,85,204)\" target=\"_blank\">Learn Behavior Design</a></font></span></b></span></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div style=\"color:rgb(136,136,136)\"><span style=\"border-collapse:collapse;font-family:Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-family:garamond,serif\"><font color=\"#888888\">&quot;the trouble is, you think you have time.</font></span></b></span><b style=\"font-family:Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:garamond,serif\"><font color=\"#888888\">&quot; --buddha \u00a0<font size=\"4\">\u00a0<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<br></font></font></span></b><span style=\"color:rgb(20,24,35);font-family:Helvetica,Arial,&#39;lucida grande&#39;,tahoma,verdana,arial,sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:17.563634872436523px\">Note: I (digitally) hand-deliver this email. So if you want out, there&#39;s no easy unsubscribe button. \u00a0You&#39;ll have to reply back via email and say &quot;please take me off.&quot; \u00a0I&#39;d rather you not, but I understand if we&#39;re not right for each other anymore.\u00a0<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n</span><b style=\"font-family:Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:garamond,serif\"><font color=\"#888888\"><font size=\"4\"><br>:).</font></font></span></b></div></div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n",
    "predicted": true,
    "read": false,
