    "message": "<div dir=\"ltr\">Will do.<div><br>Brad</div></div><div class=\"gmail_extra\"><br><br><div class=\"gmail_quote\">On Sun, May 18, 2014 at 7:26 AM, David Ngo <span dir=\"ltr\">&lt;<a href=\"mailto:dngo11@stanford.edu\" target=\"_blank\">dngo11@stanford.edu</a>&gt;</span> wrote:<br>\r\n<blockquote class=\"gmail_quote\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex\"><div dir=\"ltr\"><div><div>HaikuDeck is very clean.\u00a0 It is now my go to slide-creating site. <br><br></div>Please keep me updated on next steps with the apps. <br>\r\n<br><br></div>Happy Sunday!<br></div><div class=\"gmail_extra\">\r\n\r\n<br><br><div class=\"gmail_quote\">On Fri, May 16, 2014 at 4:35 AM, bradley Wright <span dir=\"ltr\">&lt;<a href=\"mailto:bradleywright777@gmail.com\" target=\"_blank\">bradleywright777@gmail.com</a>&gt;</span> wrote:<br><blockquote class=\"gmail_quote\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex\">\r\n\r\n\r\n<div dir=\"ltr\">Hello David,<div><br></div><div>Thank you for sending this along. It will be a helpful guide for us as we move forward, and haikudeck is certainly an interesting site.</div><div><br></div><div>We&#39;ll know more about next steps with the apps soon... and it would be great to get to work with you more.</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div><br>Thanks again for your input last week. Wonderful and sharpening.</div><div><br>Brad</div></div><div><div><div class=\"gmail_extra\"><br><br><div class=\"gmail_quote\">On Wed, May 14, 2014 at 7:31 PM, David Ngo <span dir=\"ltr\">&lt;<a href=\"mailto:dngo11@stanford.edu\" target=\"_blank\">dngo11@stanford.edu</a>&gt;</span> wrote:<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<blockquote class=\"gmail_quote\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex\"><div dir=\"ltr\">Hello gentlemen!<div><br></div><div>It was great meeting you all in person last week.\u00a0<br><div><br></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div>Apologies for the delay.\u00a0</div><div><br></div><div>I&#39;ve been wrapping up a lot of work before I go to China for a month with family.</div>\r\n\r\n<div><br></div><div>I&#39;ve included <a href=\"http://bit.ly/bdprioritymapping\" target=\"_blank\">an exclusive link to an online deck</a> for the eyes of this team only on priority mapping. Please do not share this.\u00a0</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div><br></div><div>\r\n\r\nFollowing this deck should take SoulPulse &amp; the Gratitude App to the next level. \u00a0This is normally done in person, but you all smart, and I think my instructions are clear enough.</div><div><br></div><div>During my trip like I mentioned at the end of the meeting Luke &amp; Brad,\u00a0</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div>I&#39;ll be thinking about how I can dial back my rate so that I can be more involved with the SP team. \u00a0It&#39;s something I want to contribute to.\u00a0</div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div>Happy Wednesday!</div><span class=\"HOEnZb\"><font color=\"#888888\"><span><font color=\"#888888\"><div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div><br></div>-- <br><div dir=\"ltr\"><div><div style=\"color:rgb(136,136,136)\"><span style=\"border-collapse:collapse;font-family:Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-family:garamond,serif\"><font color=\"#3333ff\"><a href=\"http://twitter.com/dngoo\" style=\"color:rgb(17,85,204)\" target=\"_blank\">David Ngo</a></font></span></b></span><span style=\"border-collapse:collapse;font-family:Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-family:garamond,serif\"><font color=\"#888888\">\u00a0|\u00a0<a href=\"http://bit.ly/behaviordesignmajor\" style=\"color:rgb(17,85,204)\" target=\"_blank\">Stanford University</a>\u00a0|\u00a0<a href=\"http://learnbehaviordesign.com\" style=\"color:rgb(17,85,204)\" target=\"_blank\">Learn Behavior Design</a></font></span></b></span></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div style=\"color:rgb(136,136,136)\"><span style=\"border-collapse:collapse;font-family:Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-family:garamond,serif\"><font color=\"#888888\">&quot;the trouble is, you think you have time.</font></span></b></span><b style=\"font-family:Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:garamond,serif\"><font color=\"#888888\">&quot; --buddha \u00a0<font size=\"4\">\u00a0</font></font></span></b></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</div></div>\r\n</div></font></span></font></span></div></div><span class=\"HOEnZb\"><font color=\"#888888\">\r\n</font></span></blockquote></div><span class=\"HOEnZb\"><font color=\"#888888\"><br></font></span></div><span class=\"HOEnZb\"><font color=\"#888888\">\r\n</font></span></div></div></blockquote></div><span class=\"HOEnZb\"><font color=\"#888888\"><br><br clear=\"all\"><br>-- <br><div dir=\"ltr\"><div><div style=\"color:rgb(136,136,136)\"><span style=\"border-collapse:collapse;font-family:Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-family:garamond,serif\"><font color=\"#3333ff\"><a href=\"http://twitter.com/dngoo\" style=\"color:rgb(17,85,204)\" target=\"_blank\">David Ngo</a></font></span></b></span><span style=\"border-collapse:collapse;font-family:Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-family:garamond,serif\"><font color=\"#888888\">\u00a0|\u00a0<a href=\"http://bit.ly/behaviordesignmajor\" style=\"color:rgb(17,85,204)\" target=\"_blank\">Stanford University</a>\u00a0|\u00a0<a href=\"http://learnbehaviordesign.com\" style=\"color:rgb(17,85,204)\" target=\"_blank\">Learn Behavior Design</a></font></span></b></span></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div style=\"color:rgb(136,136,136)\"><span style=\"border-collapse:collapse;font-family:Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-family:garamond,serif\"><font color=\"#888888\">&quot;the trouble is, you think you have time.</font></span></b></span><b style=\"font-family:Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:garamond,serif\"><font color=\"#888888\">&quot; --buddha \u00a0<font size=\"4\">\u00a0</font></font></span></b></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div></div>\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n</blockquote></div><br></div>\r\n",
