    "id": 50486,
    "message": "<html><head></head><body style=\"word-wrap: break-word; -webkit-nbsp-mode: space; -webkit-line-break: after-white-space; \">Hey Luke,<div><br></div><div>Thanks so much for getting back to me with this.... &nbsp;I totally get Bethany's taste...I pegged her as an Anthropology girl...it's one of my FAVORITE stores!!! &nbsp;This will be soooo fun....</div><div><br></div><div>Love,</div><div>Jeannine</div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div><div><div>On May 21, 2014, at 11:51 PM, Luke Knepper wrote:</div><br class=\"Apple-interchange-newline\"><blockquote type=\"cite\"><div dir=\"ltr\">Hey! Thanks so much for setting this up and being so thoughtful! She's going to love it, and it means a ton to me.<div><br></div><div>- I think she likes to bake. She did a couple times for friend's birthday parties or for fun while I was there. She hasn't been super serious about it or doing it super often, but I think she enjoys it when she does it. (By contrast, her roommate Marissa bakes almost every night. Maybe Bethany would bake more if the kitchen wasn't always occupied...)</div>\r\n<div><br></div><div>- She likes to watch movies and TV shows, to go to the gym, to read Christian books (or some other interesting ones; I know she likes Metamorphosis and one by Freud), and especially to paint and to do arts and crafts. She also spends a lot of time with friends at coffee shops, or on Pinterest.</div>\r\n<div><br></div><div>- What do you mean by really feminine things? She likes to wear dresses; she likes things with flowers on them. She's said that she is \"getting more and more feminine.\" I'd say yes. She's very feminine to me, if that means anything...</div>\r\n<div><br></div><div>- She says her favorite kind of flowers are \"flowers from Luke\" -- her favorite colors right now are coral (redish orange), white, and light green. I think she likes all kinds of flowers that look pretty.</div>\r\n<div><br></div><div>- Favorite color is definitely coral.</div><div><br></div><div>- Lots of wood / brown / black / white / creme / beige / teal. You can see our registry at <a href=\"http://myregistry.com/public/lukeandbethany\">http://myregistry.com/public/lukeandbethany</a></div>\r\n<div><br></div><div>I hope that this helps! Thanks so much for wanting to make it special for her!</div><div><br></div><div>Love, Luke</div></div><div class=\"gmail_extra\"><br><br><div class=\"gmail_quote\">On Mon, May 19, 2014 at 9:40 AM, Susan Knepper <span dir=\"ltr\">&lt;<a href=\"mailto:susanlknepper@yahoo.com\" target=\"_blank\">susanlknepper@yahoo.com</a>&gt;</span> wrote:<br>\r\n<blockquote class=\"gmail_quote\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex\"><div><div style=\"color:#000;background-color:#fff;font-family:bookman old style,new york,times,serif;font-size:14pt\"><div>\r\nHey Luke!</div><div><br></div><div style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:19px;font-family:'bookman old style','new york',times,serif;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal\">Jeannine would like more information about Bethany's tastes,&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:19px;font-family:'bookman old style','new york',times,serif;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal\"><br></div><div style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:19px;font-family:'bookman old style','new york',times,serif;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal\">\r\nDoes she like to bake?</div><div style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:19px;font-family:'bookman old style','new york',times,serif;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal\">How does she like to spend her spare\r\n time?</div><div style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:19px;font-family:'bookman old style','new york',times,serif;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal\">Does she like really feminine things?</div><div style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:19px;font-family:'bookman old style','new york',times,serif;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal\">\r\nWhat is her favorite flower?</div><div style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:19px;font-family:'bookman old style','new york',times,serif;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal\">What is her favorite color?</div>\r\n<div style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:19px;font-family:'bookman old style','new york',times,serif;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal\">What colors are you registering for in the home?</div><div style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:19px;font-family:'bookman old style','new york',times,serif;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal\">\r\n<br></div><div style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:19px;font-family:'bookman old style','new york',times,serif;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal\">Please \"Reply All.\"</div><div style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:19px;font-family:'bookman old style','new york',times,serif;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal\">\r\n<br></div><div style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:19px;font-family:'bookman old style','new york',times,serif;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal\">xoxo</div></div></div></blockquote></div><br></div>\r\n</blockquote></div><br></div></body></html>",
