    "message": "<div dir=\"ltr\">Looks pretty good! I asked for a quote for 50 people for the rehearsal dinner -- should be &#39;nuf for family and close friends.<div>Have a great camping trip if I don&#39;t talk to you before you leave.</div>\r\n<div>-Dad</div></div><div class=\"gmail_extra\"><br><br><div class=\"gmail_quote\">On Fri, May 23, 2014 at 1:14 PM, Luke Knepper <span dir=\"ltr\">&lt;<a href=\"mailto:lukeknepper@gmail.com\" target=\"_blank\">lukeknepper@gmail.com</a>&gt;</span> wrote:<br>\r\n<blockquote class=\"gmail_quote\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex\">Hey! Here are the photos and videos that Charity took. The place looks really really cool! Thank you for finding it and for setting this up!<br>\r\n\r\n<br>\r\nLove, luke<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<br></blockquote></div><br><br clear=\"all\"><div><br></div>-- <br><br><div>-Chris</div><div><br></div><div>cell: 703-419-0231 \u00a0| \u00a0<a href=\"http://twitter.com/csknepper\" target=\"_blank\">twitter.com/csknepper</a></div><div>\r\n<br></div>\r\n</div>\r\n",
